How to run the tests for dmemo (Distributed Memory)
===================================================

Case 1: No MPI, no GPI

Just run the serial tests

./dmemoTest

Case 2: MPI, no GPI

- Default communicator will be MPI
- run the tests for different number of processors

mpirun -np 1 ./dmemoTest
mpirun -np 2 ./dmemoTest
mpirun -np 4 ./dmemoTest

Case 3: GPI, no MPI

- Default communicator will be GPI
- run the tests for different number of processors

gaspi_run -np 1 ./dmemoTest
gaspi_run -np 2 ./dmemoTest
gaspi_run -np 4 ./dmemoTest

Case 4: MPI + GPI

- Default communicator will be MPI 
- It is not possible to identify default communicator by mpirun or gaspi_run

export SCAI_COMMUNICATOR=MPI

...  // as case 2 

export SCAI_COMMUNICATOR=GPI

...  // as case 3
